description: Inspect and test the internal circuit of control module 4 to check for internal faults such as a failed switch, blown trace, or open connection, specifically with all switches ON., outcome='All switches, cables, and connections in control module 4 show nominal continuity, and no internal open circuits or faults are detected. No polarity inversions were found in the inspected connections (all (+) and (−) cables are connected to corresponding polarity ports). All measured resistances are within expected nominal values.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=170.0, cost_breakdown=[('close_switch', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('test_continuity', 20.0), ('test_continuity', 20.0), ('test_continuity', 20.0), ('test_continuity', 20.0), ('test_continuity', 20.0)], simplified_outcome=None)] 
